narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments:
Strengths: making us develop our own project meant we were attached and invested in the work we were doing and really extended our knowledge
Weakness: more clear instructions of tasks at hand

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, learning about UNICEF programming for global child health issues from the expert Dr. Alipui is a privilege. Students get to research into often neglected issues and think of solutions -- a unique practicum course!
Yes - if you are interested in development and Africa then this course really helps extend your knowledge
